      • isEligibleProperty

        protected boolean isEligibleProperty(String key,
                         Object value)
        Determine whether the given model element should be exposed as a query property. The default implementation considers Strings and primitives as eligible, and also arrays and Collections/Iterables with corresponding elements.. This is changed behavior from Spring 2.0, so we always return true for backward compatibility.
